END, [x.ProductTags].[TagId]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [x.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x2].[Id]
    FROM [Products] AS [x2]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.ProductCategory2] ON [x2].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory2].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

END, [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[TagId]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[Id], [t8].[Id0], [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Products] AS [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [x5].[Id], [x.Product.ProductCategory5].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BillDetails] AS [x5]
        INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [x.Size5] ON [x5].[SizeId] = [x.Size5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Products] AS [x.Product5] ON [x5].[ProductId] = [x.Product5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.Product.ProductCategory5] ON [x.Product5].[CategoryId] = [x.Product.ProductCategory5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [x.Color5] ON [x5].[ColorId] = [x.Color5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [x.Bill5] ON [x5].[BillId] = [x.Bill5].[Id]
        WHERE [x5].[BillId] = @__billId_0
    ) AS [t8] ON [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t8].[Id0]
) AS [t9] ON [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t9].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t9].[Id], [t9].[Id0], [t9].[Id1]" (0723d8ff)
